{"tid":2258861,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"好羨慕表哥","createTime":"2020-10-26T11:07:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-26T15:32:35.000Z","uid":349136,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6fce5f5b1ab918dc27e7f2a12b79bd88e39a9646","tid":2258861,"uid":349136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T11:07:19.000Z","msg":"點解有啲人嘅人生可以咁順利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n表哥佢由細到大都好叻 人又幽默<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nDse考得幾好讀咗科唔錯嘅科<br />\nGrad咗就3萬一個月<br />\n依家26,7歲5,6萬一個月<br />\n佢有一個靚嘅女朋友 個樣好甜 好純<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2個都係返醫院 一齊努力 奮鬥<br />\n係對方嘅初戀 拍咗7年拖 <br />\n依家要準備結婚了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解佢嘅路好似一直都咁順利<br />\n相反我 2幾歲 仲讀緊HD 同時要搵錢交學費<br />\n初戀就比人帽 依家驚咗拍拖<br />\n做咩都有阻滯咁 好多麻煩野 人又蠢<br />\n又唔靚 唔可以好似啲靚女求其嫁人做幸福少奶奶<br />\n仲要父母就退休 細妹殘障要養埋佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以前好迷失嘅時候真係好想死咗去就算<br />\n覺<br />\n但諗起仲有屋企人要養點都要捱落去<br />\n今日聽到表哥就結婚單野真係喊咗出嚟 <br />\n太羨慕喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"187e0cf55e94c8675c14aea798991d56d67232ec","tid":2258861,"uid":9392,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T11:10:59.000Z","msg":"見到人仆街我就拍手 見到人不幸我就慶幸 見到人靚仔過我就想佢死全家 見到人有錢過我就訓住公屋咒佢破產跳樓死 哈哈哈哈哈哈哈唔路唔唔哂咩哈口"},{"pid":"1fbef899360d851ee9a5234bb8289b105c941c63","tid":2258861,"uid":349136,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"187e0cf55e94c8675c14aea798991d56d67232ec","tid":2258861,"uid":9392,"like":1,"dislike":1,"sco